  <brief_title>A Study Assessing the Efficacy and Safety of DE-127 Ophthalmic Solution in Subjects With Mild or Moderate Myopia (APPLE)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, Randomized, Double-Masked, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel-Group Study Assessing the Efficacy and Safety of DE-127 Ophthalmic Solution Compared With Placebo in Subjects With Mild or Moderate Myopia (APPLE)</official_title>
